name: South_Shore_Pure_Black_Axess_5-shelf_Narrow_Bookcase
reviews: It fits the space I needed it to and holds all the books I needed it too, but it's pretty wobbly and putting it together stained my hands black... I placed it so it isn't touching any walls with its painted sides.
description: Place this lofty Axess five-shelf bookcase in an office or living room to keep your personal reading collection organized and in good condition. The tall, slender profile is ideal for rooms with limited floor space while providing ample shelving to house your reading material or decorative accents.
